"""Few-shot style examples — permanent, hidden from the user.
Used ONLY as internal style reference for the LLM when generating:
- Nota MedSys de Hospitalización (piso)
- Nota MedSys de UTI/UTIM
- Mensajes de WhatsApp para el médico tratante

These are the "gold standard" of the surgical residency service.
They must NEVER be shown to the user, never be copied verbatim, and never
be treated as clinical data. The LLM must learn ONLY: structure, order,
tone, vocabulary, length and the way information is integrated.
"""

